data.description: This single story home features 4 bedrooms, and 2 full bathrooms. Upon entering, you'll be greeted with an open entry and hallway leading to two secondary bedrooms and full bathroom. Continuing further into the home, you'll find the living room that flows easily into the kitchen and eat-in dining area, making for the perfect entertaining space. Another small hallway off of the kitchen leads to a convieneint third bedroom and the laundry room. The large primary suite is located privately towards the rear of the home and offers a generously sized primary bathroom and spacious closet. This home has been meticulously maintained and is an easy commute to Lackland AFB, Sea World, shopping and more! **VA Assumable at 2.875%**
